  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Sunday</h2>The Sunday is a short walkthrough horror game where the idea of being alone will hunt you, until the drakness settles in your brain. <strong>The line between reality and nightmare is razor thin.</strong><br>You wake up hangover after a party, alone. Your parents took a short trip to visit one of your relatives that is sick. It only takes a little time until the <strong>voices start to become a part of the reality.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126440/extras/98ce84a64a74d136c3cd3577ae07fa6a.poster.avif?t=1729792870\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126440/extras/98ce84a64a74d136c3cd3577ae07fa6a.webm?t=1729792870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126440/extras/98ce84a64a74d136c3cd3577ae07fa6a.mp4?t=1729792870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Gameplay</h2>The Sunday is a first-person walkthrough horror simulator, so the main mechanic is <strong>exploration</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>- </strong>Horror ambience</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>- </strong>Relistic graphics</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>- </strong>Ambient light</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>- </strong>Dialogues with NPCs</ul>",
